Organization: Northwestern University, Evanston Illinois.
Date: Wed, 12 Aug 1992 15:06:59 GMT
Lines: 690

Hi everyone!

This is Game 7.  After tim and fmc, people on IGS are probably expecting
*tweet* next -- yes, this game is dedicated to *tweet*.  Who's tweet?  Let
me put it this way: tweet to IGS is like the Godfather to the Mafia. :-)
He was involved in the establishment of all three existing Go servers, so
it's not surprising that tweet knows everything on IGS.  And tweet knows
everything on IGS for one single reason -- he does his best to serve everyone.

Thank you, tweet. *bow* :)

jzy NR ^_^

P.S. I apologize that I have not mentioned a tiny yet important detail
about viewing these Dang Hu Games.  If you want to read the game, please
cut the part below the following line and save *that* part to some file and
view it with mgt.  If you include the part above the line in your mgt file,
you might run into some bugs, such as the setup stones might be skipped.

------------------------- 8< cut here >8 -----------------------------

