Comment[White wins.

Overview: At the beginning, B's attack at the lower left was successful, thus B began to lead.  B's mistakes \(#70 and #86\), however, cost him the lead.  W played very well afterwards: #93 and #95's sharp attack, and #99's great thinking put W on the winning track.  Later, during W's invasion to B's left and B's invasion to W's top, both players showed tremendous skills.  A spectacular game indeed.]
